Changes in version 1.6.6
------------------------

  - Add 'show_logFC' and 'show_all_cols' options to 'topTable'.


Changes in version 1.5.6
------------------------

  - Update 'diffcyt()' wrapper function to handle new SingleCellExperiment object 
    structure from CATALYST.


Changes in version 1.3.17
-------------------------

  - Add additional optional arguments for methods 'testDA_edgeR', 'testDS_limma', and 
    'testDS_LMM'.


Changes in version 1.3.12
-------------------------

  - Allow selecting columns of 'experiment_info' with character vector of column names, 
    when creating design matrix or model formula.


Changes in version 1.3.6
------------------------

  - Renamed and extended summary table function 'topTable' (previously 'topClusters').


Changes in version 1.0.0
------------------------

  - Initial version available from Bioconductor.
